# Network Traffic Analysis Project (Wireshark)

## Overview
Analyzed a PCAP file using Wireshark to identify suspicious network activity.

## Key Findings
- Detected SYN Flood (DDoS attack) targeting port 80
- Identified brute force attempts over SSH (port 22)
- Analyzed traffic patterns and IP behavior

## Tools Used
- Wireshark

## Skills Demonstrated
- Network traffic analysis
- Threat detection
- Packet filtering
